1. *Kosa* joj je bila plava. (Her hair was blonde.)
2. *Kose* su joj padale preko ramena. (Her hair was falling over her shoulders.)
3. Ona je svoju *kosu* češljala pred ogledalom. (She was brushing her hair in front of the mirror.)
4. Ona je nosila *kosu* u punđi. (She was wearing her hair in a bun.)
5. *Kosi* je vetar pomalo pomerio. (The wind slightly moved her hair.)
6. Ona je prešla rukom preko svoje *kose*. (She ran her hand through her hair.)